  "story": {
    "title": "A Strange Discovery",
    "body": "Rina was sitting in the library among her friends. They were working on a school project about the universe. She looked at a chart showing different planets. Suddenly, she saw something strange in the sky through the window. A dark cloud moved quickly, and an alien shape appeared. She could not comprehend what she saw at first. She tried to describe it to her friends, but they did not believe her. She felt nervous but stayed calm. Instead of running, she decided to write a report about it. Later, her teacher said it was a rare view of a new planet. Everyone was surprised. Rina did not fail her project. She got a good grade and felt proud.",
